{"id":183468,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/09/global-voices-伊朗：用艺术抢救湖泊/","date":"2011-09-27T19:30:33Z","modified":"2011-09-27T19:30:33Z","title":"Global Voices | 伊朗：用艺术抢救湖泊","content":"<p><p>星期一伊朗亚塞拜然区内<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ardabil\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ardabil\">阿尔达比勒</a>的抗议群众再度<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2011/08/28/iran-protests-to-save-lake-urmia-reignited/\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2011/08/28/iran-protests-to-save-lake-urmia-reignited/\">走上街头</a>，要求政府拯救<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lake_Urmia\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lake_Urmia\">尔米亚湖</a>。伊朗博客报导了几个亚塞拜然活跃分子遭到打压及逮捕。</p>\n<p>当局<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.eurasiareview.com/11092011-iran-allow-peaceful-protests-over-lake’s-destruction/\" href=\"http://www.eurasiareview.com/11092011-iran-allow-peaceful-protests-over-lake%E2%80%99s-destruction/\">最近承诺</a>将拨款约九千五百万从邻近河川引水，复原世界最大咸水湖之一的尔米亚湖。</p>\n<p>Goftar Sabz 目击了阿尔达比勒星期一发生的事件。他在博客上<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://goftaresabz.wordpress.com/2011/09/12/دستگیری-10-نفر-از-معترضان-در-اردبیل/\" href=\"http://goftaresabz.wordpress.com/2011/09/12/%D8%AF%D8%B3%D8%AA%DA%AF%DB%8C%D8%B1%DB%8C-10-%D9%86%D9%81%D8%B1-%D8%A7%D8%B2-%D9%85%D8%B9%D8%AA%D8%B1%D8%B6%D8%A7%D9%86-%D8%AF%D8%B1-%D8%A7%D8%B1%D8%AF%D8%A8%DB%8C%D9%84/\">写道</a>：</p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.facebook.com/pages/%DA%AF%D8%B1%D9%88%D9%87-%D8%AD%D9%85%D8%A7%DB%8C%D8%AA-%D8%A7%D8%B2-%D8%AD%DB%8C%D8%A7%D8%AA-%D8%AF%D8%B1%DB%8C%D8%A7%DA%86%D9%87-%DB%8C-%D8%A7%D8%B1%D9%88%D9%85%DB%8C%D9%87/197463140318427#!/pages/%DA%AF%D8%B1%D9%88%D9%87-%D8%AD%D9%85%D8%A7%DB%8C%D8%AA-%D8%A7%D8%B2-%D8%AD%DB%8C%D8%A7%D8%AA-%D8%AF%D8%B1%DB%8C%D8%A7%DA%86%D9%87-%DB%8C-%D8%A7%D8%B1%D9%88%D9%85%DB%8C%D9%87/197463140318427\"><img title=\"Stay blue - protest art for Lake Urmia\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/abi-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"Stay blue - protest art for Lake Urmia\" width=\"225\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<p>“维持湛蓝” —— 脸书上的尔米亚湖抗议艺术。</p>\n</div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>傍晚大约六点我在阿尔达比勒走着，街上布满了安全部队。两名抗议人士在呼口号时遭到逮捕。我走向沙里亚提广场，一路上看到十个人被逮捕。听说其他地方还有更多人被维安部队逮捕。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Sev-news 博客<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://sev-news.blogspot.com/2011/09/blog-post_12.html\" href=\"http://sev-news.blogspot.com/2011/09/blog-post_12.html\">写道</a>：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>阿尔达比勒有数场示威抗议，網絡速度趋近于零，也无法用行动电话联系。群众持续抗议，并呼口号保卫尔米亚湖。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Kolekhabar <a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://kolekhabar.blogspot.com/2011/09/iranpressnews-iranpressnews_2833.html\" href=\"http://kolekhabar.blogspot.com/2011/09/iranpressnews-iranpressnews_2833.html\">写到</a>几天前维安部队在数名活跃份子家中将其逮捕并没收了他们的私人物品。</p>\n<p>Rah Azadi <a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://2000azadi.blogspot.com/2011/09/blog-post_7475.html\" href=\"http://2000azadi.blogspot.com/2011/09/blog-post_7475.html\">说</a>阿尔达比勒像是被占领了一样，到处都是维安部队。</p>\n<p>尔米亚湖支持者也建立了<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.facebook.com/pages/گروه-حمایت-از-حیات-دریاچه-ی-ارومیه/197463140318427#!/pages/گروه-حمایت-از-حیات-دریاچه-ی-ارومیه/197463140318427\" href=\"http://www.facebook.com/pages/%DA%AF%D8%B1%D9%88%D9%87-%D8%AD%D9%85%D8%A7%DB%8C%D8%AA-%D8%A7%D8%B2-%D8%AD%DB%8C%D8%A7%D8%AA-%D8%AF%D8%B1%DB%8C%D8%A7%DA%86%D9%87-%DB%8C-%D8%A7%D8%B1%D9%88%D9%85%DB%8C%D9%87/197463140318427#%21/pages/%DA%AF%D8%B1%D9%88%D9%87-%D8%AD%D9%85%D8%A7%DB%8C%D8%AA-%D8%A7%D8%B2-%D8%AD%DB%8C%D8%A7%D8%AA-%D8%AF%D8%B1%DB%8C%D8%A7%DA%86%D9%87-%DB%8C-%D8%A7%D8%B1%D9%88%D9%85%DB%8C%D9%87/197463140318427\">脸书页面</a>，目前已有超过四千七百名追踪者。在其中一个脸书群组图片（上图）上写着：“维持湛蓝”。</p>\n<p>脸书上还有其他的艺术创作，像下图则是呼唤“当人们无能漠视，请老天保佑”。</p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.facebook.com/pages/%DA%AF%D8%B1%D9%88%D9%87-%D8%AD%D9%85%D8%A7%DB%8C%D8%AA-%D8%A7%D8%B2-%D8%AD%DB%8C%D8%A7%D8%AA-%D8%AF%D8%B1%DB%8C%D8%A7%DA%86%D9%87-%DB%8C-%D8%A7%D8%B1%D9%88%D9%85%DB%8C%D9%87/197463140318427#!/pages/%DA%AF%D8%B1%D9%88%D9%87-%D8%AD%D9%85%D8%A7%DB%8C%D8%AA-%D8%A7%D8%B2-%D8%AD%DB%8C%D8%A7%D8%AA-%D8%AF%D8%B1%DB%8C%D8%A7%DA%86%D9%87-%DB%8C-%D8%A7%D8%B1%D9%88%D9%85%DB%8C%D9%87/197463140318427\"><img title=\"Lake Urmia protest art\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/abi4.jpg\" alt=\"Lake Urmia protest art\" width=\"280\" height=\"396\" /></a></p>\n<p>尔米亚湖抗议艺术</p>\n</div>\n<div>校对：<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"使用者:Soup\" href=\"http://proj.daodin.net/mediawiki/index.php/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E8%80%85:Soup\">Soup</a></div>\n<p><span>作者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/author/hamid-tehrani/\" title=\"文章导读 Fred Petrossian\">Fred Petrossian</a> · 译者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/author/hllee/\" title=\"文章导读 Hsu-Lei Lee\">Hsu-Lei Lee</a> </span><br />\n · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2011/09/14/iran-protest-art-to-save-lake-urmia/\" title=\"阅读原文  [en]\">阅读原文  [en]</a> · <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/2011/09/28/9870/#comments\" title=\"则留言\">则留言 (0) </a></span><br />分享: <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.hemidemi.com/user_bookmark/new?title=%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%EF%BC%9A%E7%94%A8%E8%89%BA%E6%9C%AF%E6%8A%A2%E6%95%91%E6%B9%96%E6%B3%8A&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2011%2F09%2F28%2F9870%2F&#038;description=&#038;via=sticker\" title=\"HEMiDEMi\"><span>HEMiDEMi</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://myshare.url.com.tw/index.php?func=newurl&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2011%2F09%2F28%2F9870%2F&#038;desc=%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%EF%BC%9A%E7%94%A8%E8%89%BA%E6%9C%AF%E6%8A%A2%E6%95%91%E6%B9%96%E6%B3%8A\" title=\"MyShare\"><span>MyShare</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.shouker.com/%22%20onclick=%22javascript:var%20js=document.createElement%20(\" title=\"Shouker\"><span>Shouker</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.facebook.com/share.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2011%2F09%2F28%2F98